akka.japi.pf

Class FI

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.japi.pf.FI

  • public final class FI
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that encapsulates Functional Interfaces used for creating partial functions. These classes are kept for compatibility, but for future API's please prefer the ones in akka.japi.function.
